1. Add entity-framework to your project
2. Define how your data model should look like
3. Create the DataContext
4. Enable-Migrations in the PackageManager console
5. Add-Migration MigrationName (MigrationName is a name that you give to describe what you have done)
6. Update-Database in the PackageManager console
7. Use DataAnnotations in order to specify how EF should behave if you do not want the default behaviour